Quadcopter

- Taranis X9D
- X8R receiver
- CC3D Revolution Flight Controler
- U-Blox Neo M8N GPS
- Frame
- Motors
- ESC
- Propellers
- Battery
- Alarm
- OpLink
- Power distribution
- OpenPilot ground station


Goals :
- Telemetry in ground station and remote control
- GPS assisted flights
- FPV

Design:
Connection diagram
CC3D initial configuration
Telemetry link to the ground station
Flight modes configuration
Failsafe (receiver and flight controler)
Calibration (Accel, Gyros, Magneto, Level)
Tip : resurect firmware

